  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382820/extras/a2f644289619cfa4c716f2faf7fb0311.avif?t=1774442327\" width=600 height=84 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you know what is better than robbing banks? Robbing banks with your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invite up to 3 friends to join you in your criminal endeavor!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382820/extras/8fac5021062f659ea2b079cf86717f91.avif?t=1774442327\" width=600 height=84 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Robbing the same bank over and over again gets boring at some point. That's why many features like position of cameras, guards and objectives will be randomized for each playthrough.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This means every heist will feel a little different!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382820/extras/a46387dea472722cc286a19c6bb6ccf7.avif?t=1774442327\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes not everything goes to plan - if you (or one of your accomplices) triggers the alarm you have to bail!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once the cops arrive it's over. No shooting your way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382820/extras/218a55fe405700e2f7588f25b5103d8d.avif?t=1774442327\" width=600 height=84 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No real guard would patrol the whole night between point A and point B and point C...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guards will get hungry, thristy or go to the toilet. And you can use that to your advantage!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382820/extras/a2f644289619cfa4c716f2faf7fb0311.avif?t=1774442327\" width=600 height=84 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you know what is better than robbing banks? Robbing banks with your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invite up to 3 friends to join you in your criminal endeavor!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382820/extras/8fac5021062f659ea2b079cf86717f91.avif?t=1774442327\" width=600 height=84 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Robbing the same bank over and over again gets boring at some point. That's why many features like position of cameras, guards and objectives will be randomized for each playthrough.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This means every heist will feel a little different!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382820/extras/a46387dea472722cc286a19c6bb6ccf7.avif?t=1774442327\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes not everything goes to plan - if you (or one of your accomplices) triggers the alarm you have to bail!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once the cops arrive it's over. No shooting your way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382820/extras/218a55fe405700e2f7588f25b5103d8d.avif?t=1774442327\" width=600 height=84 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No real guard would patrol the whole night between point A and point B and point C...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guards will get hungry, thristy or go to the toilet. And you can use that to your advantage!</p>",
